title: Hermes_test
---
<<Fade "#000000" 1 0 0.6>>        // fade back in
<<PlayAudio "Romance">>  
<<Scene "lounge bg draft 3">>
<<Act "Aelius" "Aelius 3_4s" "left" "bottom">>
Aelius: Hey, welcome in.

<<Act "Hermes" "Hermes 3_4" "right" "bottom">>
Hermes: Hi there, can I get a—

Hermes: Wait, you're new here.
Aelius: Yes, my name's Aelius, I'm the new cook. Hestia hired me. Today's my first day.
Hermes: Well hello then, Aelius. I'm Hermes.
Hermes: But I assume you already guessed that.
Aelius: I had my suspicions.
Hermes: (Sarcastic) Very clever of you.
Hermes: I'm in a hurry, kid — not much time to chat. Could you whip me up a hamburger? Quickly, please.
Aelius: You got it. I'll do my best.

<<StartCooking "MakenaTestScene">>

<<jump Hermes_test_Success>>
===

title: Hermes_test_Success
---
<<Scene "lounge bg draft 3">>
<<Act "Aelius" "Aelius 3_4s" "left" "bottom">>
Aelius: Got your hamburger ready as fast as I could.
Aelius: Hopefully this goes better than the other two…
Aelius: Or at least better than Zeus. *sigh*
Aelius: Hope you like it.

<<Act "Hermes" "Hermes 3_4" "right" "bottom">>
Hermes: Thanks, Aelius. Looks great!
Hermes: Only wish I had time to sit and enjoy it.
Hermes: But duty calls — messages to deliver. You get the gist.

Aelius: …
Hermes: Rough first day?
Aelius: You could say that.
Hermes: Let me guess — Zeus stopped in.
Aelius: How did you know?
Hermes: Call it intuition. He's very good at ruffling newcomers' feathers.
Aelius: I cooked his food to perfection; he still didn't seem to want me here.
Hermes: Listen, Aelius: ignore him. Do your best. Show him you're up to snuff.
Aelius: It's not that easy—
Hermes: I really have to go. See you around!

<<Hide "Hermes">>
<<set $hermes_day1_done = true>>
===


title: Hermes_test_Fail
---
Aelius: Sorry — that took longer than I hoped—
Hermes: No time. I have to run.
<<Hide "Hermes">>
Aelius: Well, that was… something.
<<set $hermes_day1_done = true>>
===



